did u check the pop reports?
Thromdog, you made me laugh out loud. I appreciate it
I think there are a number of good fits so far as auction houses go.  It's the type of card a lot of people might be looking for actively. I would look at history and you'll get a good feel.

Nice card! 

I'm sure any of the good auction houses (Sterling, Brockelman & Luckey, Love of the Game, etc..) would be interested in having you consign. Should be some strong interest for back collectors, Baltimore collectors, etc...
POP = 2 and this is the high graded one. So, knowing T206 collectors as I am learning to do..... I would guesstimate, 1 millllllion dollars. Bwhahahaha
Thanks for all the great info guys. As always, this board comes through with the best advice, info and ideas
